How to set everything up on ubuntu:

* install mysql: apt-get install mysql-server
* login to the mysql server as root and do:

  create database [dbname]
  grant all privileges on [dbname].* to '[user]'@'localhost' identified by '[password]'

* install django: apt-get install python-django python-mysqldb
* install git: apt-get install git-core git-svn
* fork the 821plus github repository;
  git clone <cl
